---
title: Cajun Chicken Traybake with broccoli and roast potatoes
description: This traybake might be a snap to prepare, but that doesn't mean it's not filled with flavour. Between golden roast potatoes, tender broccoli, soft sweet carrots and juicy chicken breast, this is a dish that's definitely minimal effort for maximum reward.
